#: src/2421-unreservations-2018.md:15
msgid "Motivation"
msgstr ""

#: src/2421-unreservations-2018.md:18
msgid ""
"We are currently not using any of the reserved keywords listed in the "
"[summary](#summary) for anything in the language at the moment. We also have "
"no intention of using the keywords for anything in the future, and as such, "
"we want to unreserve them so that rustaceans can use them as identifiers."
msgstr ""

#: src/2421-unreservations-2018.md:23
msgid "Guide-level explanation"
msgstr ""

