msgid "See the [reference-level-explanation](#reference-level-explanation)."
msgstr ""

#: src/2421-unreservations-2018.md:28
msgid "Reference-level explanation"
msgstr ""

#: src/2421-unreservations-2018.md:33
msgid ""
"The keywords listed below are removed from the [list of reserved keywords]"
"(https://doc.rust-lang.org/book/second-edition/appendix-01-keywords."
"html#keywords-currently-in-use) and are longer reserved such that they can "
"be used as general identifiers. This is done immediately and on edition 2015."
msgstr ""

